title: Database Link Unavailable (http://cenhancer.chenzxlab.cn/)
body:
Thank you for developing such a great database! I wanted to bring to your attention that the link to the database server appears to be unavailable. I have been trying to access it via http://cenhancer.chenzxlab.cn/, but it seems that the connection is no longer active.

Could you kindly look into this issue when you have time? I would be grateful if the access could be restored. I look forward to your response.

Thanks,
